  "detailed_description": "Fisticubes is a goofy physics-based one-button boxing party game where up to 4 players compete to destroy each other!<br><br><u>Enjoy such features as:</u><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Single-player tournament mode! 1v1 your way to the championship!<br></li><li>Online multiplayer with Steam's Remote Play Together<br><br></li><li>A growing selection of different arenas!<br></li><li>Plenty of match-making options!<br></li><li>2-4 player support with customizable controls!<br></li><li>Anvils that destroy the very floor beneath you!<br></li><li>Bombs that launch you in any and every direction!<br></li><li>Vegetables that make you grow bigger than your enemies!<br></li><li>Springs that launch you upwards to get the drop on your foes!<br></li><li>Colour Blind Accessibility!<br></li><li>Bots for offline and friendless play!<br></li><li>First-person mode!*<br></li><li>Virtual-reality mode!* ** ***</li></ul><br><u>Credits:</u><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Artwork by Bethany Coyles<br></li><li>Music by The Flaming Pike<br></li><li>Trailer by Josh Curry-Glasper</li></ul><br>*First-person mode & virtual-reality mode are only available in the single-player tournament mode.<br>**Please ensure you have enough space around you to avoid hitting objects and/or walls and take all necessary precautions before using VR mode!<br>***VR mode is limited at this time and still in development.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1651360/extras/71476d5703d163808e3dde1797bde93e.poster.avif?t=1679933021\" width=292 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1651360/extras/71476d5703d163808e3dde1797bde93e.webm?t=1679933021\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1651360/extras/71476d5703d163808e3dde1797bde93e.mp4?t=16799330